show.title: Love Me If You Dare
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/YtVzqp
show.description: Love me If You Dare is a powerful psychological drama that follows Navami, a young woman trapped between ambition and exploitation. Working in a resto pub, her life takes a dark turn when she encounters Abhinav, a charming yet controlling man whose obsession blurs the line between desire and dominance. As Navami faces harassment, betrayal, she struggles to reclaim her dignity and identity. Through pain and resilience, she transforms from a victim into a voice of strength.
